Class Condition

    • net.hudup.core.data.Profile

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Condition
extends Profile
    Condition is the special profile which is used in condition clause where in SQL statement for processing database, for example. Note that SQL is formal programming language used for querying, updating, processing objects in database. However condition can be used in any necessary situation.
